creator: BRO PASSENGER SERVICES L.L.C
descriptionHtml:
Bro application specializes in individual delivery services, we strive through the pro delivery application to build a solid foundation that inspires everyone, simplifies and improves people's lives. Bro works as a delivery app in regions with high smartphone penetration and younger populations, where technology can play a bigger role in developing economies than in more developed regions of the world.
Bro offers Local technical solutions to improve transportation and banking services in the region as we strive to grow from a car booking, transportation and delivery service to one of the best applications that the user relies on in his daily life.
Our unique approach to transportation solutions allows easy-to-use options, and with the negotiation of trip prices, passengers and drivers are free to negotiate the terms of the deal based on price, route or other factors.
Bro faces many of the inequalities that characterize mass transportation, including abstract algorithms, price manipulation and harsh conditions for service providers (drivers).
Our management
Our leaders are working hard to develop our program and move it forward through the use of technology and the creation of new jobs. In this growing economy, we call the drivers we work with to provide transportation services (captains), which is an easy way to encourage respect for the work they do.
As our company grows to become more than just a car rental company, our leaders ensure that the culture of helping others is maintained by leaving their mark on everyone's life.
Rely on pro anytime, everywhere
One of the most important advantages of the Bro application is its wide spread and presence throughout the Arab world ... This allows you to get the fastest possible connection with the highest levels of comfort and security ... And get the rest at the lowest cost.
With pro you always win
Bro charges the captain the lowest commission for the flight... This provides the captain with the highest possible profit he can get from one trip... This is in addition to the many gifts and points that Bro provides for each captain... Such as discounts on commission... And trips without Commission.
Enjoy new benefits from Bro
Transparency of flight conditions
All travel conditions are determined by real-time interactions between drivers and passengers, without being subject to any opaque or uncontrollable algorithms that manipulate prices.
The cost is always lower
Travel and excursion costs in Bro are always lower than our competitors, this is because models based on real-time quotes can help us determine the optimal cost compatible with passengers and driver partners.
Direct payments
Travelers pay Bro partners directly (in cash). This allows us to reduce costs and maintain lower fare values than our competitors, while being able to easily add captain's earnings.
Safety and security
Ride with Bro and rest assured that all our partner service providers have been verified in advance, approved and approved after verifying all their data, for more peace of mind Bro offers you in-app security features, secure payment methods and round-the-clock Captain Support all days of the week.
We are reimagining the way we make the world a better place
Mobility is our specialty ... It is our lifeline, and we cannot live without it, it makes us active to go to work every morning, and allows us to invent new and better ways to solve transportation and delivery problems.
It's all for you ... Go to all the places you want and with Bro.
Excursions and other services
In addition to helping passengers move with ease and with the greatest comfort and safety, we help people to complete their business and accomplish their interests quickly and affordably, create new transport solutions, and help companies provide a smooth mobility experience for employees. And always help delivery partners (drivers) to achieve the highest return on their time investment.

descriptionHtml:
Request a ride, track & share driver’s route in real time and reach destination, hassle-free.
BRO was created out of the desire to enhance urban mobility while prioritizing safety, convenience, and affordability.
Our goal was to create a user-centric platform that caters to the diverse needs of our riders, ensuring every trip to be as comfortable as can be.
Whether you're commuting to work & regular destinations, going out for the night, booking trip for a family member, or simply heading out for an
errand, BRO is your perfect choice for your every day's ride.
BRO strives to uplift the ride-hailing offerings by providing a multitude of impressive features that raise the bar for both riders & drivers.
BRO app offers an unparalleled level of convenience right at your fingertips.
Ride with BRO!
Safety & convenience are our top priority at BRO, where we have implemented a high measures recruitment & training process that only allows the most
reliable and experienced drivers to our community, to ensure that your journey is not only enjoyable but also completely safe.
Furthermore, we are committed to reducing our carbon footprint and create a greener future, where we promote the use of electric and hybrid vehicles
in our fleet, prioritizing eco-friendly transportation options whenever possible.
BRO caters to your budgetary needs with a transparent and competitive pricing model, ensuring that you always get the best value for your money. Our
app provides upfront fare estimates, allowing you to plan your expenses accordingly. No more worrying about fluctuating prices or hidden charges – with
BRO, it is all about the journey, not the destination.
Join our “Host Drivers”
Being the host of each and every ride, you play a main role in making every journey safe and enjoyable for our riders.
At BRO, we believe in creating a positive and rewarding experience for our Host drivers, that are considered a main success partner.
Here's how we do our best to add value to their journey with BRO
1.Manage your working hours: choose your own working hours. Whether you prefer to drive during peak hours or in your spare time.
2.Transparent earnings: With our detailed earnings reports, you can easily track and monitor your earnings on a daily basis.
3.Support and Safety: Your safety and well-being are our top priorities. We have a dedicated support team available 24/7 to assist you with any
questions or concerns you may have, to ensure the smoothest work environment we could possible provide
